item.title: Stress Relief Fair
item.author: postdoc@ucr.edu (UCR PostdocAssoc)
item.description: The RPA, in association with GradSuccess and the UCR's Health Promotion Department (The Well) , invites the postdoctoral community (postdoctoral/visiting scholars and project scientists) to the Spring 2023 Stress Relief Fair on Tuesday, April 25, 2023, at the Physics Courtyard.
